{
  "stem": "15721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And but-- when I was then a graduate from high school at age 19, I enrolled in [INAUDIBLE], the liberal rabbinic seminary in Berlin, and arrived there on May 1st, 1935, and began my rabbinic studies at that point.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Germany, you had a choice of three different types of high schools.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mind you, they were all nine schools.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You made that decision.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or that decision was really made for you, because when you were nine years old, you didn't really know what your life should be like.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in my instance, my parents decided that I should go to what was known as the humanist high school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a high school that had an emphasis on ancient languages-- nine years of Latin, six years of Greek, just to-- just for starters.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had only one modern language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was an elective.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took a couple or three three years of, of English at the end of my high school life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we went to school from 8:00 in the morning till 12:40 and sometimes still 1:20.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And if you took any electives, they were in the afternoon, such as music, or language, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was the typical middle European education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And well, it has stood me in good stead in many ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had, for instance, seven years of history, and I think nine years of geography.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't even remember it all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the best of my knowledge, there was one other in my class that I know for sure.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think there was any other.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
